    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c0dbc5ed9dd8284d5dd10b7"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "IU has very long arms into the Federated Suns' government Commander, besides contributing to Hanse Davion's propaganda machine, and they might even be working together with the NAIS in the most top secret projects.\n\nOne of them might be testing a new weapon of mass destruction based on HPG principles, based on what you have previously seen on Mirfak during my rescue from the Lone Wolves.",
      "branches": [
