    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cbc80014e4546da90f673a5"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "You have evidence of the 'null bomb'?\n\nWeapons that can interfere with HPG communications and interstellar travel are theoretical, there was never evidence that anyone has ever worked on them.\n",
      "branches": [
