      "text": "That is what I suspect might have happened there and in other locations, a test of that weapon, against single JumpShips and Periphery systems, causing temporary blackouts and delays that can be easily dismissed since the HPG waves can propagate through several star systems.\n\nBut now with the Fourth Succession War in progress, the KF weapon has been deployed close to an exposed Liao border.",
